com.mariner.datamerge.model

Class DataRecord

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mariner.datamerge.model.DataRecord

  • public class DataRecord
extends Object
    The DataRecord model object encapsulates a unified representation of records found in each file format. ( JSON, CSV, and XML ). Typically, this object would follow the Data transfer object ( DTO ) design pattern, as it does not have any specific behavior defined except for storage, retrieval, formatting, serialization and deserialization of its own data. See Data Transfer Object
    Author:
    Maryse Arseneau
